### âœ… Exercise 1: Basic User model

1. Set up a new Prisma project with SQLite/Postgres
2. Create a `User` model:

   ```prisma
   model User {
     id    Int    @id @default(autoincrement())
     name  String
     email String @unique
   }
   ```
3. Generate the client
4. Create a script to:

   * Add a new user
   * Fetch all users
   * Find a user by email

